title: Episode 321: DAMN! His Momma Ugly (Feat. Justina Valentine & Makaela)
itunes:title: Episode 321: DAMN! His Momma Ugly (Feat. Justina Valentine & Makaela)
description:
Rapper/actress, Justina Valentine, and Singer, Makaela join the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote their latest singles and EP's. Justina just dropped her single. 'That that Pic,' while Makaela is pushing her 'Me and Somebody's Son' EP, as well as her newest single 'Comfortable.' The ladies discuss what they think the highlight to their sex tape would be...and Justina went OFF. Makaela opens up about her struggle to find a man tall enough for her, Gigi gives an update on her vagina rejuvenation, and much more. Enjoy!
